---
layout: layout
title: "{dev.talk} - Speakers"
description: "Meet the incredible speakers who have shared their knowledge and experience at {dev.talk} meetups in the south of the UK."
permalink: speakers.html
includeBlueskyPosts: true
---

<section>
  <h1 id="speakers">
    <a href="#speakers">Our Speakers</a>
  </h1>
  <p>
    A huge thank you to every speaker who has shared their knowledge, stories, and expertise with the {dev.talk} community. You make these events possible.
  </p>
  <aside class="speakers-call-to-action">
    <h2>Want to become a speaker?</h2>
    <p>All experience levels welcome—from lightning talks to in-depth sessions. We'll help you with ideas, structure, and practice.</p>
    <a href="https://sessionize.com/dev-talk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="speakers-cta-button">Submit Your Proposal on Sessionize</a>
    <p><a href="/call-for-speakers.html">View full speaker guidance</a></p>
  </aside>
  <div class="speakers-grid">
    {% for speaker in speakers.all %}
      <div class="speaker-card">
        {% if speaker.bioPicUrl %}
          <div class="speaker-card-image">
            {% if speaker.url %}
              <a href="{{ speaker.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <img src="{{ speaker.bioPicUrl }}" alt="{{ speaker.name }} headshot" loading="lazy" class="speaker-card-headshot">
              </a>
            {% else %}
              <img src="{{ speaker.bioPicUrl }}" alt="{{ speaker.name }} headshot" loading="lazy" class="speaker-card-headshot">
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="speaker-card-body">
          <h2 class="speaker-card-name">
            {% if speaker.url %}
              <a href="{{ speaker.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ speaker.name }}</a>
            {% else %}
              {{ speaker.name }}
            {% endif %}
          </h2>
          {% if speaker.jobTitle %}
            <p class="speaker-card-job">{{ speaker.jobTitle }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          {% if speaker.bio %}
            <p class="speaker-card-bio formatted-description">{{ speaker.bio }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="speaker-card-sessions">
            <h3>{{ 'Sessions' if speaker.sessions | length > 1 else 'Session' }}</h3>
            <ul>
              {% for sess in speaker.sessions %}
                <li>
                  {% if sess.videoUrl %}
                    <a href="{{ sess.videoUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ sess.title }}</a>
                  {% else %}
                    {{ sess.title }}
                  {% endif %}
                </li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
